  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1770577205\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1770577205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1770577205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Also this is kind of demo of the game.</strong> Game is a dark, atmospheric adventure that immerses you in a world of shadows, secrets, and choices. Blending elements of psychological horror, narrative exploration, and survival horror, Game offers immersive experiences designed to keep players on their toes from the first encounter.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/d7118ad9a26792e5a0a7ba5119b7d17b.poster.avif?t=1770577205\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/d7118ad9a26792e5a0a7ba5119b7d17b.webm?t=1770577205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/d7118ad9a26792e5a0a7ba5119b7d17b.mp4?t=1770577205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll embark on an unnerving journey of isolation, mystery, and danger. The environments are meticulously designed to tell their own story ruins, woods, forgotten landscapes marked by evidence of a strange memory or neglected whispers. Everything is atmospheric and designed to impress with curiosity and fear as you unveil pieces of the underlying hidden truth.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/086549fbea871d4cf11876cbc97c860d.poster.avif?t=1770577205\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/086549fbea871d4cf11876cbc97c860d.webm?t=1770577205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/086549fbea871d4cf11876cbc97c860d.mp4?t=1770577205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game is not about stupid jump scares or cheap scares. Rather, \"BrahmaRakshas Abandon Village\" is about building tension through exploration, filmic experiences, and encounters that challenge your temerity. You will get to experience whether it is solving environmental puzzles, illuminating uncomfortable lore, or just existing with what lurks in darkness. Most importantly, the game values patience, observation, and gut.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/947187c8ed48c6347b694245666edd83.poster.avif?t=1770577205\" width=548 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/947187c8ed48c6347b694245666edd83.webm?t=1770577205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/947187c8ed48c6347b694245666edd83.mp4?t=1770577205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/2af39211d7891c5d392a5e78ed8b1102.avif?t=1770577205\" width=400 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>By</strong> <strong>EerieEchoGames</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1770577205\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1770577205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1770577205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Also this is kind of demo of the game.</strong> Game is a dark, atmospheric adventure that immerses you in a world of shadows, secrets, and choices. Blending elements of psychological horror, narrative exploration, and survival horror, Game offers immersive experiences designed to keep players on their toes from the first encounter.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/d7118ad9a26792e5a0a7ba5119b7d17b.poster.avif?t=1770577205\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/d7118ad9a26792e5a0a7ba5119b7d17b.webm?t=1770577205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/d7118ad9a26792e5a0a7ba5119b7d17b.mp4?t=1770577205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll embark on an unnerving journey of isolation, mystery, and danger. The environments are meticulously designed to tell their own story ruins, woods, forgotten landscapes marked by evidence of a strange memory or neglected whispers. Everything is atmospheric and designed to impress with curiosity and fear as you unveil pieces of the underlying hidden truth.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/086549fbea871d4cf11876cbc97c860d.poster.avif?t=1770577205\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/086549fbea871d4cf11876cbc97c860d.webm?t=1770577205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/086549fbea871d4cf11876cbc97c860d.mp4?t=1770577205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game is not about stupid jump scares or cheap scares. Rather, \"BrahmaRakshas Abandon Village\" is about building tension through exploration, filmic experiences, and encounters that challenge your temerity. You will get to experience whether it is solving environmental puzzles, illuminating uncomfortable lore, or just existing with what lurks in darkness. Most importantly, the game values patience, observation, and gut.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/947187c8ed48c6347b694245666edd83.poster.avif?t=1770577205\" width=548 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/947187c8ed48c6347b694245666edd83.webm?t=1770577205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/947187c8ed48c6347b694245666edd83.mp4?t=1770577205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331980/extras/2af39211d7891c5d392a5e78ed8b1102.avif?t=1770577205\" width=400 height=300 /></span></p>